          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Does the White Card cover home health care?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Yes. The White Card covers physician-ordered home health services — including skilled nursing, wound care, therapy, and home health aide services — at no out-of-pocket cost for approved EEOICPA beneficiaries."
